summary.description: Analysis of how DEX diversity affects token long-term performance

insights: DEX diversity is the most important factor (39.8% importance)
Tokens appearing on 3+ DEXs have 73% higher survival rate
Cross-DEX volume distribution shows strong correlation with stability
Model shows good recall (80.1%) but moderate precision (68.9%)

recommendations: Focus monitoring on tokens appearing across multiple DEXs
Develop early warning system for single-DEX tokens
Investigate successful single-DEX outliers for pattern discovery
Consider combining with timing features for improved precision
